1
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:10,100
♪I love the clarity in your eyes♪

2
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:13,860
♪Like a shooting star across my world♪

3
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Repeating the goodbye we never said♪

4
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:21,540
♪Through sleepless nights♪

5
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:25,100
♪I miss the way you looked at me♪

6
00:00:25,700 --> 00:00:30,260
♪Like photos freezing that summer bit by bit♪

7
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:35,380
♪By the shore with warm winds, maybe we'll meet again♪

8
00:00:37,380 --> 00:00:41,460
[Fall in Love Again]

9
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:43,980
[Episode 1]

10
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:06,200
I don't believe I can't get him this time.

11
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,120
Mr. Fu,

12
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,320
I've done everything you asked.

13
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:28,760
When will you keep your promise?

14
00:01:29,290 --> 00:01:30,320
You don't trust me?

15
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:32,550
Yet you still deal with me?

16
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,720
Of course I do.

17
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:39,960
My body and my heart are yours.

18
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,160
Okay.

19
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:49,960
Moving on.

20
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,360
Get ready for the next scene.

21
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,260
Okay.

22
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:54,670
Give it to me.

23
00:01:54,670 --> 00:01:56,180
All departments, prep the next scene!

24
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,160
- Thanks. - Props, pack up.

25
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,560
- Prep the next scene. - Good work, everyone.

26
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,240
Wait outside for me.

27
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:05,880
Okay, Yu.

28
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:06,660
I'll wait outside.

29
00:02:19,250 --> 00:02:20,200
You scared me.

30
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:24,720
I just saw you kissing He Zheng.

31
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,240
You were really into it.

32
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,360
What?

33
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,320
You like him?

34
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:31,760
Jealous?

35
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:36,320
He's just an unknown actor.

36
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,480
With you here,

37
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,760
why would I look at him?

38
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,080
That's more like it.

39
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:58,520
Hello, Xi.

40
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,620
- Everyone, gather up. - Hello.

41
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:00,610
- Three people over here. - Hello, Xi.

42
00:03:00,610 --> 00:03:01,100
Okay.

43
00:03:02,930 --> 00:03:04,990
Makeup, quick touch-up for the actor.

44
00:03:05,380 --> 00:03:06,140
On it!

45
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:07,100
Xi.

46
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:09,160
Um, let's double-check.

47
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,210
There are four.

48
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,080
Xi, what brings you here?

49
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,720
Aren't you wrapping today?

50
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,560
I came to check in.

51
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:18,120
I brought milk tea and desserts,

52
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:18,950
get someone to pick them up.

53
00:03:18,950 --> 00:03:19,660
- Thanks. - Okay.

54
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,280
Here's water.

55
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,480
Gaffer, I need you here now!

56
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:23,960
Hello, Xi.

57
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:24,860
Hello, Xi.

58
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:26,560
Where's Director Qi?

59
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,480
- What are you here for? - Get in touch now.

60
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,880
He's giving notes to the cast.

61
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:30,480
I'll go get him for you.

62
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,320
No need. He's in the lounge, right?

63
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,520
I'll go myself.

64
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,880
- You do your thing. - Two people over here.

65
00:03:35,810 --> 00:03:37,320
- You'll handle this later. - Move over a bit.

66
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:37,780
Okay.

67
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,360
Qi, do you love me?

68
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,000
Yes, yes, of course I do.

69
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,760
If you love me, don't marry her.

70
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,160
Alright?

71
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,040
Marrying her

72
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,960
is just to satisfy the public.

73
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,280
Otherwise the image I built

74
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:03,560
would fall apart.

75
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,000
You only think about yourself,

76
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,640
never about me.

77
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,800
How could I not think about you?

78
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,240
The female lead in my next drama

79
00:04:14,450 --> 00:04:15,520
is still you.

80
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:18,300
Really?

81
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:19,980
Of course.

82
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,000
How will you repay me?

83
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:42,000
Chu Jingxi.

84
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,440
You are?

85
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,840
I'm He Zheng.

86
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,040
The male lead of this show.

87
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,060
Thanks for your hard work. Milk tea and desserts outside.

88
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:55,770
Ms. Chu.

89
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:56,650
Go over there.

90
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:57,960
Set it a bit farther.

91
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,660
Anything else?

92
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,320
I like you.

93
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:03,960
I'm your fan.

94
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,160
I've liked you for years.

95
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,560
May I get your autograph?

96
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,850
You startled me.

97
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:10,960
Where should I sign?

98
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:11,450
Coming.

99
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,040
Here.

100
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:17,920
On your clothes?

101
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:23,100
[To: He]

102
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:41,060
[To: He Zheng — May all your wishes come true]

103
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:42,760
Good luck.

104
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,560
You just...

105
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,320
I didn't interrupt, did I?

106
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,760
Honey, what brings you here?

107
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,120
I heard you're wrapping today.

108
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,400
So as the boss's wife,

109
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,120
I came to show some support.

110
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,160
Xi is so kind.

111
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:05,880
Thank you.

112
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,240
You're welcome.

113
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,760
What scene were you discussing?

114
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:19,760
It seemed intense.

115
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:28,720
Yu was doing an argument scene.

116
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,560
I gave her some pointers.

117
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,440
The emotions went a bit too far,

118
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,960
so things got a little messy.

119
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,160
By the way, honey.

120
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,720
How's the wedding prep going?

121
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,640
I'm on set every day.

122
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,160
I haven't been much help.

123
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,360
Just focus on filming.

124
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,120
I've got things covered at home.

125
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,600
Be mindful of your image out there.

126
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,960
You're a leader, after all.

127
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,960
Director Qi, I'll head out first.

128
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,720
I won't interrupt your sweet moment.

129
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,240
Yu,

130
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,560
I brought your favorite tiramisu.

131
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,840
I'll have the assistant bring it over.

132
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,360
I'm cutting sugar lately.

133
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,320
I don't want to age faster.

134
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,560
I'll pass.

135
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,360
A little won't hurt.

136
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:09,720
Xi,

137
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,010
you haven't acted in a long time.

138
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,320
You wouldn't get our struggles.

139
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,240
I'll go get ready.

140
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,350
What's with Yu?

141
00:07:24,350 --> 00:07:25,640
- She's acting weird. - Just leave it.

142
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,320
Honey, I haven't seen you in days.

143
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,440
I've missed you.

144
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,520
Focus on work.

145
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:33,160
Okay.

146
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:35,800
Honey.

147
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:36,800
By the way,

148
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,600
the son-conceiving remedy my mom gave you,

149
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,570
have you been taking it?

150
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:43,320
I don't want it—it's too bitter.

151
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,160
Honey,

152
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,360
please bear with it,

153
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,600
since we're trying for a baby, right?

154
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,000
I've got it all planned.

155
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,320
For our honeymoon,

156
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:53,840
I'll take you where you want to go.

157
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:54,960
The Maldives.

158
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,320
Really?

159
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,120
Really.

160
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,680
Director, the actor has changed outfits.

161
00:08:00,690 --> 00:08:01,640
Okay, got it.

162
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:02,920
Then you get back to work.

163
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:03,760
I won't interrupt.

164
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,400
I've got a lot to handle at home.

165
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,160
Work hard.

166
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:10,880
I'm heading out.

167
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:11,440
Go ahead.

168
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,560
Yang,

169
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,440
come help me.

170
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:29,280
Okay.

171
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:30,640
Let go.

172
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,750
Does this look straight?

173
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,840
A little more to the left.

174
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:43,360
Like this?

175
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:43,960
Okay.

176
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:44,920
All set?

177
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,720
All set.

178
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:51,160
You're like a perfect rose.

179
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:53,600
How did you end up in the wrong vase?

180
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,560
That's a terrible analogy.

181
00:08:57,930 --> 00:08:59,530
Hey, be careful.

182
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:02,160
You're a grown-up,

183
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,560
but you still act like a child.

184
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,320
Mom.

185
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,240
What does your mother-in-law mean by that?

186
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,280
Pregnant?

187
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,080
What are you talking about?

188
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,000
It's too soon.

189
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:13,120
Too soon?

190
00:09:13,490 --> 00:09:15,960
No, it's not.

191
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,840
Anyway, you don't have a job.

192
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:24,960
So after the wedding,

193
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,560
you might as well stay home and have a baby.

194
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,720
Who says

195
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,400
that once she's married, she must stay home and have kids?

196
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,320
And who says Chu has no job?

197
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,760
Everything your son has today

198
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:36,890
comes from Chu's resources and connections.

199
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,800
Even if she's not working right now,

200
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,160
it's because your son is insecure

201
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,200
and won't let her be seen.

202
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,160
Yang,

203
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:44,850
Mom and Qi mean well.

204
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,360
I mean well, don't I?

205
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,000
Chu.

206
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,450
Let me be clear.

207
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,800
Our family has its rules.

208
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,520
After you're married,

209
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:59,080
see less of those questionable friends,

210
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:01,240
so they don't affect my son.

211
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,000
Who are you calling questionable?

212
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:03,840
Mom.

213
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,920
Did you bring that remedy for a son?

214
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,440
You're willing to drink it?

215
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:11,960
Okay.

216
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,360
I'll go get it now.

217
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:14,600
I'll grab it right away.

218
00:10:15,860 --> 00:10:17,120
I'll go get it for you now.

219
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,120
Seriously?

220
00:10:18,350 --> 00:10:20,080
- A mother like that? - It's fine, it's fine.

221
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:21,690
- A person like that? - Don't be mad.

222
00:10:21,690 --> 00:10:23,690
- And she's your future mother-in-law. - Okay, don't be mad.

223
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,680
Oh my god, she called me questionable?

224
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,600
She was the one inappropriate!

225
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,920
Alright, don't get so angry.

226
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,280
Listen to me.

227
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,120
A troublemaking mom-in-law,

228
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,760
and a macho guy.

229
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,800
Plus all his scandals.

230
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:36,640
I'm telling you,

231
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,600
this marriage,

232
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,760
you should think it through.

233
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:39,440
Yang.

234
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,960
You're a top agent in our circle

235
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,840
and you believe gossip like that?

236
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:46,000
When you were my agent,

237
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,840
how many made-up scandals did you fix for me?

238
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:48,640
Have you forgotten?

239
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,120
Fine, let's say 80 percent.

240
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,840
80 percent of it is fake,

241
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:55,000
but that leaves 20 percent that doesn't add up.

242
00:10:55,170 --> 00:10:55,640
Right?

243
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:59,040
Yang, since I chose to love him,

244
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,400
I have to trust him.

245
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:02,030
For the first thirty years,

246
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,200
I had no family.

247
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,940
I didn't even know who my parents were.

248
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:07,920
Now,

249
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:10,240
I've finally found my happiness.

250
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,120
You should be happy for me.

251
00:11:12,470 --> 00:11:15,120
Silly girl, I just want you happy.

252
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,360
I want what's best for you.

253
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,400
But you!

254
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,200
You, I...!

255
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,160
Forget it.

256
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,000
I hope I'm wrong.

257
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,160
Yang,

258
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:32,170
you're my only family.

259
00:11:32,810 --> 00:11:34,930
I want your blessing.

260
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:36,980
Alright.

261
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,160
Then today,

262
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:41,040
we'll toast with water instead.

263
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,000
Wishing you both happiness.

264
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,120
Thank you.

265
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,120
- Cheers. - Cheers.

266
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,360
To a lifetime together.

267
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,120
Okay.

268
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:01,960
Please welcome our beautiful bride.

269
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,560
Over here, over here.

270
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:16,560
Miss, look at the camera.

271
00:12:20,380 --> 00:12:21,440
Ms. Chu, over here.

272
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,770
- Over here. - Ms. Chu.

273
00:12:22,770 --> 00:12:23,720
- One more. - Look at the camera.

274
00:12:39,690 --> 00:12:41,440
He surprised me,

275
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,950
I'll surprise him too.

276
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:46,000
Chu, whatever you do,

277
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:46,960
I support you.

278
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,080
The bride looks stunning.

279
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:01,840
Someone's dream girl is marrying another man,

280
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,640
too bad the groom isn't him.

281
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,240
How does that make you feel?

282
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,080
Get lost!

283
00:13:12,530 --> 00:13:14,810
I wish the earth were flat,

284
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,360
so I could keep looking

285
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,040
and still see you.

286
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,760
Only see you.

287
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:25,760
Fits the classic line from "Fleet of Time", right?

288
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,160
As long as she's happy.

289
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,320
Chu,

290
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:46,040
I started from the bottom

291
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:49,040
and climbed my way up, step by step, to where I am today.

292
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,040
Everything I have now

293
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:54,040
thanks to your support and for being by my side.

294
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,960
And above all, I'm grateful

295
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,720
to have someone as amazing as you in my life.

296
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:01,200
So please believe in me,

297
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,200
I'll love you properly

298
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,120
and cherish you.

299
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:07,050
Well said!

300
00:14:07,050 --> 00:14:10,750
- Yes! - Well said!

301
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,400
You should've cherished me.

302
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,120
But you didn't.

303
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,120
Have you lost your mind?

304
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:30,360
This is my wedding.

305
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,840
Isn't this the madness you like?

306
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:33,920
Alright, Yu.

307
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:34,720
Let's stop this.

308
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,160
I want to be your bride

309
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,960
before Chu Jingxi does.

310
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:46,800
You little tease.

311
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,680
This wedding's off, let's go!

312
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:20,840
I can't leave.

313
00:15:47,700 --> 00:15:50,660
♪When clouds sink into the deep sea♪

314
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:53,940
♪Ripples spread♪

315
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:57,020
♪Traces of a racing heart♪

316
00:15:57,860 --> 00:16:00,500
♪Is it the sky or its reflection♪

317
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:03,980
♪I can't tell anymore♪

318
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:08,300
♪Lost in your eyes♪

319
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:13,820
♪As we draw closer♪

320
00:16:14,820 --> 00:16:16,980
♪The space of an embrace♪

321
00:16:17,580 --> 00:16:20,180
♪Scatters the dark♪

322
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:24,460
♪When the wind comes, raise the sails♪

323
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:26,740
♪And sail on♪

324
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:32,300
♪Miles ahead are no longer a dream♪

325
00:16:33,180 --> 00:16:38,180
♪Where even migratory birds can't reach, you're by my side♪

326
00:16:39,180 --> 00:16:43,980
♪Then I can spread my wings and fly with courage♪

327
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:49,740
♪If storms rise, I'll follow your light♪

328
00:16:51,260 --> 00:16:55,580
♪Trusting we'll reach a warm shore♪

329
00:16:56,340 --> 00:17:01,340
♪Where even migratory birds can't reach, you're by my side♪

330
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:07,820
♪I'll break through the haze and run toward what I once longed for♪

331
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:12,860
♪Even if I'm hurt, I won't wander alone♪

332
00:17:14,460 --> 00:17:17,260
♪You're where my heart belongs♪

